Uses of Package
arrayGenerator

  • Packages that use arrayGenerator 
    Package Description
    arrayGenerator
    ArrayGenerators are objects that generate arrays of integers.
    arraySorter
    ArraySorters are objects that provide a sort method that will sort arrays of Comparables.
    stringSearcher
    String searchers will search for the first occurrence of a given substring in superstrings.
  • Classes in arrayGenerator used by arrayGenerator 
    Class and Description
    ArrayGenerator
    Defines the interface for classes that generate arrays of arbitrary types
    ArrayGeneratorTest
    Provides some basic tests for array generators: Do the generators generate arrays of the correct size? Do the generators throw the expected negative array size exception if asked to generate an array of negative size?
    ScopedArrayGenerator
    A scoped array generator generates arrays in which the generated elements fall within a certain Scope.
    ScopedArrayGeneratorTest
    Implements additional tests, in addition to those inherited from ArrayGeneratorTest, to check that: Values in generated arrays are within the specified scope All values in the scope are generated.

  • Classes in arrayGenerator used by stringSearcher
